        <abstract>
            <p>Looks forward to a visit from JVC and family in August.</p> 
<p>Sheets of vol. 1 of <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi> [2d ed.] are going to printer;</p>  
<p>new edition of <hi rend="italic">Coral reefs</hi> is half printed.</p> 
